    <div class="box-text">Your weight fluctuates by 2–4 lbs day to day based on water retention, sodium, carbs, and hormones. One number on one morning tells you nothing. What matters is the trend over 2–3 weeks. We track weight, measurements, and photos together — because together they tell the truth.</div>
